RELEASE NOTES This is GENSYMCID-1881, regression test for GENSYMCID-983 'action-button name box'
BACKGROUND In some G2 versions, action-button name-box does not change when the name of the action-button change.
SOLUTION We used pre-existing test kb. We had to use player to find the name-box on the workspace (found no way to obtain it with G2 language).
TESTING Test fails in G2 FY2013-R03 Ent and passes in HIP2016-09
NOTES When test is started, persistent change is made to the name of action-button. Use "Change name of button (Undo)" button on benchmark-test sub-workspace to revert it.
It is a library of test-related utilities. Those can be moved out to a separated module, but that's too early yet
